Title: Operation Mind Control 
Author: Walter Bowart
Published Date: 1978
Ebook Format: EPub

This is an investigative report into government mind control programs. Through the use of drugs such as LSD, behavior modification, hypnosis, and other 'psycho-weapons' people in top secret U.S Government roles experimented on the public and military personnel. From these experiments the most advanced technology was created and still in use today on people of the world so that governments can have control over the mind to continue the enslavement of the human race.
